gw.cc.bizrules

Class ActivityRulesPermissionProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.cc.bizrules.ActivityRulesPermissionProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IRulePermissionProvider

    public class ActivityRulesPermissionProvider
extends java.lang.Object
implements IRulePermissionProvider
    ActivityRulesPermissionProvider is the main api used to access the permissions by the business rules framework. These Permissions are defined in the CC layer and then used by the framework to permit users to perform business rules related tasks.
